<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Save Nature</title>

    <style>
        body{
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #e8f5e9;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        header{
            background-color: green;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .container{
            width: 80%;
            margin: 30px auto;
            background-color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px gray;
        }

        img{
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        p{
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        button{
            background-color: green;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            font-size: 18px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        button:hover{
            background-color: darkgreen;
        }

        footer{
            background-color: green;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <header>
        <h1>Save Nature, Save Future</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="container">

        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1441974231531-c6227db76b6e?w=800" alt="Nature">

        <h2>Why Nature is Important?</h2>

        <p>
            Nature provides us with fresh air, clean water, food, and shelter.
            Trees help reduce pollution and make our environment healthy.
            Protecting nature is essential for the survival of future generations.
        </p>

        <p>
            Every small action such as planting trees, saving water, and reducing plastic use
            can make a big difference in protecting our planet.
        </p>

        <button onclick="showMessage()">Join the Green Mission</button>

    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2026 Nature Awareness Campaign</p>
    </footer>

    <script>
        function showMessage() {
            alert("Thank you for supporting the Green Mission! 🌱");
        }
    </script>

</body>
</html>
